Job Title: Senior Backend Python Engineer

We are hiring a Senior Backend Python Engineer to build and scale API-driven services for a SaaS platform.

Must-have skills:
- Python
- FastAPI
- PostgreSQL
- Docker
- AWS

Nice-to-have skills:
- Kubernetes
- Terraform
- GitHub Actions
- Observability (metrics, logging, tracing)

Responsibilities:
- Design and ship production-grade microservices.
- Improve API performance, reliability, and fault tolerance.
- Own data models and SQL query efficiency.
- Collaborate with product and frontend teams.
- Participate in on-call and incident response.

Experience:
- 4+ years of backend engineering experience.
- Strong software design and clean-code practices.
